    "name": "Mapama Pirates",
    "steam_appid": 1701080,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/937761e1d9342e5948b6c0dc782cdae9.avif?t=1771792035\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras_big/937761e1d9342e5948b6c0dc782cdae9.avif?t=1771792035 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在<i>Mapama</i>的无尽世界中，这是一款充满<strong>冒险</strong>、<strong>海战</strong>和<strong>宝藏</strong>的<strong>MMO</strong>游戏！驾驶你自己的<strong>船只</strong>，航行在辽阔的大海上，靠岸于<strong>多个港口</strong>，为你的船员补给、进行贸易并升级你的船只。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将从一艘小巧的单桅<strong>单桅帆船（Sloop）</strong>开始，装备两门火炮。但只要你聪明地收集木材、矿石和其他资源，就能不断<strong>升级你的船只</strong>。逐步提升为强大的<strong>双桅帆船（Ketch）</strong>，甚至掌控巨大的<strong>战舰（Galeon）</strong>或<strong>护卫舰（Fregatte）</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/2f84dfbe50138239ea3d856f9fb7da14.poster.avif?t=1771792035\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/2f84dfbe50138239ea3d856f9fb7da14.webm?t=1771792035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/2f84dfbe50138239ea3d856f9fb7da14.mp4?t=1771792035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Mapama的世界中，你可以掌握各种<strong>职业</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    木工 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    冶金 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    海战 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    航海术 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    捕鱼 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    贸易 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在所选职业中等级越高，技能就越<strong>强大</strong>：例如更快采集稀有资源、更高效的海战，或在港口获得更好的交易。你的成功取决于你的专业能力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/8c1fd252f0f7b0af03ae21ab84374731.poster.avif?t=1771792035\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/8c1fd252f0f7b0af03ae21ab84374731.webm?t=1771792035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701080/extras/8c1fd252f0f7b0af03ae21ab84374731.mp4?t=1771792035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大海充满了<strong>危险与秘密</strong>：挑战强大的幽灵船、抢劫敌方商队、寻找宝藏，或带领你的船员前往未知的海岸。勇敢者还可以参与<strong>PvP战斗</strong>，与其他玩家一决高下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友组队，或加入一个<strong>公会</strong>。你们可以一起影响港口的价格，甚至<strong>征服整座城市</strong>。在队伍中，金币和经验会公平分配，在海上一起冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的船就是你的生命——用更好的船帆、更强大的火炮和华丽的舰首装饰来升级它。你的每一个决定，都会让你更接近终极的海盗船长之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扬帆起航，在<i>Mapama</i>的风暴海洋中成为一段传奇！</p>",
